{"tid":2102524,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"那些年，我們一起打過的噴嚏","createTime":"2020-07-10T13:49:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-14T07:01:24.000Z","uid":134103,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"f25a48e606e4a17fcc1458db5d164a5cf34f4bc7","tid":2102524,"uid":134103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T13:49:12.000Z","msg":"今日睇咗優先場，套戲好麻麻，唔睇冇損失，如果無聊冇嘢做想消磨下時間都勉強可以入場睇下<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/solution.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我覺得成套戲冇一個角色能夠令人留低特別深刻嘅印象，男女主角、配角(古天樂、王大陸、徐子珊)、音波俠、大奸角全部都好鳩下鳩下，冇乜特色咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n以愛情片嚟講，柯震東嗰種熱血大笨蛋式追求愛情嘅大男孩角色喺那些年已經睇過一次，好有既視感，再加上那些年嘅劇本完整過呢套好多，所以呢套戲嘅愛情線其實麻麻地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n以英雄片嚟講，啲CG同打鬥都幾hea<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />而且英雄片嘅元素唔係幾夠，睇得出導演係想拍用英雄片做包裝嘅愛情片，但係內核嘅愛情元素又拍得麻麻，搞到有啲不倫不類<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後結局仲有一種趕收工、草草結尾嘅感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n以下開放討論"},{"pid":"7df7dc9e6596ad222f57014fcff10fd7405e6eae","tid":2102524,"uid":322685,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T14:09:43.000Z","msg":"睇咗trailer <br />\n柯震東好似那些年咁係咁係到嗌<br />\n好嘈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27410a8947a947142216da9bb7f973a9e8f92133","tid":2102524,"uid":134103,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"7df7dc9e6596ad222f57014fcff10fd7405e6eae","tid":2102524,"uid":322685,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T14:09:43.000Z","msg":"睇咗trailer <br />\n柯震東好似那些年咁係咁係到嗌<br />\n好嘈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T17:02:06.000Z","msg":"係，其實嗰一幕其實睇到好尷尬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src