":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T03:49:26.000Z","msg":"啲剪接過場好似睇得tvb膠劇咁<br />\n<br />\n仲有大陸近年喜劇式嘅笑話，真係完全笑唔出<br />\n將雙手放入邊爐拎啲料出黎再疊高，點解我睇果場咁多人笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57db5b9a3a570ab256f757d39d3e1efd49293811","tid":2102524,"uid":25245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T03:56:44.000Z","msg":"為左林依晨入場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但套嘢真係太鳩 睇多次高登三寶是但一套好好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7aced171d1de578d26e573bd1b69e2866e194d1","tid":2102524,"uid":378,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T07:01:24.000Z","msg":"覺得少年心心仲正過林依晨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}